ifconfig/ip: Display network configuration.
netstat: Network statistics.
ss: Socket statistics.
ping: Test network connectivity.
tar: Tape Archive — Compress and archive files.
gzip/gunzip: Compress/decompress files.
who: Display who is logged in.
w: Display who is logged in and what they are doing.
last: Show last logged in users.
whoami: Display the current username.
su: Switch user or become a superuser.
groups: List user’s group memberships.
newgrp: Change the effective group ID.
id: Display user and group information.
chpasswd: Change passwords in batch mode
